description: [``botocore``] This release contains API changes that enable users to configure their Amplify domains with their own custom SSL/TLS certificate.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for AWS Chatbot. You can now monitor, operate, and troubleshoot your AWS resources with interactive ChatOps using the AWS SDK.
[``botocore``] Documentation updates for the AWS Config CLI
[``botocore``] Changed description for latencyMode in Create/UpdateChannel and Channel/ChannelSummary.
